<h5></h5>

Dust Logger images from boreholes 21, 50, 66, 52, 10, 2, 86 and 14 were taken between 2004 and 2011 (Fig. 1).  Using these data, we can reconstruct provisional dust profiles for every string in the array.  Accounting for the distortions and fine structure in dust could <A HREF="http://icecube.wisc.edu/~dima/work/WISC/ppc/fit/tilt/model/">improve the detector model</A>.
